.TH LOA-STATS 1 "2026-03-15" "Library Of Alexandria" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
stats \- Show aggregate library statistics
.SH SYNOPSIS
alexandria> stats
.SH DESCRIPTION
.TP
Shows totals (including book vs sheet-music split), read/unread split, reading list count, monthly/yearly progress, location counts, average rating, and top genres/tags.
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
alexandria> stats
.SH SEE ALSO
loa(1), loa-sheet-stats(1)
.SH AUTHOR
Generated for the Library Of Alexandria project.
